videos.headline: Snell fumbles on Kentucky's first play
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. coughs it up on the Wildcats' first play that turns into a field goal for the Volunteers.

videos.headline: Tempers flare with the Wildcats and Volunteers
videos.description: Kentucky and Tennessee push and shove after a kickoff return, resulting in two unsportsmanlike conduct penalties.

videos.headline: Chandler runs right through a defender
videos.description: Ty Chandler breaks open a 29-yard run after delivering a huge hit to a defender.

videos.headline: Snell picks up 2nd TD
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr.'s long run sets up a short touchdown for the Wildcats running back.

videos.headline: Chandler caps off Volunteers' drive with TD
videos.description: Ty Chandler finishes a 7-play, 75-yard drive with a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Snell barrels in for 3rd TD
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. extends the Wildcats' lead with a 1-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Chandler gets 2nd 1-yard TD
videos.description: Ty Chandler makes it a one-point game after his second 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jones looks for poise out of team in 2nd half
videos.description: Butch Jones wants to trade field goals for touchdowns in the second half.

videos.headline: Johnson leaves game after 34-yard gain
videos.description: Kentucky starting quarterback Stephen Johnson exits the game after a 34-yard run.

videos.headline: Vickers forces 4th Wildcats' fumble
videos.description: Kendal Vickers forces a fumble from Garrett Johnson as the Volunteers are set up with great field position.

videos.headline: Richardson tip-toes on the sideline
videos.description: Tavin Richardson pulls down a 16-yard catch on the sideline all while staying in bounds.

videos.headline: Johnson goes Superman to put UK in the lead
videos.description: Stephen Johnson takes it in from 11 yards out for the touchdown, and the Wildcats convert the 2-point conversion to lead 29-26 with 30 seconds to go.

videos.headline: Tennessee falls 3 yards short of Hail Mary victory
videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano finds Jeff George on the Hail Mary pass, but George is tackled on the 3-yard line as Tennessee falls to Kentucky 29-26.

videos.headline: Stoops talks about Kentucky's 29-26 win over Tennessee
videos.description: Mark Stoops discusses what this win means to the program and fans and how his team battled hard.
